### Casino API Examples
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/health

### Register User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "handle": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "handle": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Get All Games
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games

### Get Game Configuration
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/candle_flip

### Preview Bet
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bets/preview
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "game": "candle_flip",
  "currency": "USDC",
  "stake": "10.00",
  "params": {
    "prediction": "red"
  }
}

### Place Bet (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bets/place
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "game": "candle_flip",
  "currency": "USDC",
  "stake": "10.00",
  "clientSeed": "my_client_seed_123",
  "params": {
    "prediction": "red"
  }
}

### Get Bet Details (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bets/BET_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Resolve Bet (admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bets/resolve/BET_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Cashout Bet (for crash games)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bets/cashout/BET_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Get User Bets (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/bets?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Get Wallet Balances (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/wallets
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Get Balance for Specific Currency (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/wallets/balance?currency=USDC
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Faucet (Demo Mode Only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/wallets/faucet
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "currency": "USDC",
  "amount": "100.00"
}

### Get Ledger Entries (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/wallets/ledger?currency=USDC&limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Get Current Fairness Seed (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/fairness/seed/current
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Rotate Fairness Seed (admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/fairness/seed/rotate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Reveal Fairness Seed (admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/fairness/seed/reveal
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "seedId": "SEED_ID"
}

### Verify Fairness
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/fairness/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serverSeed": "revealed_server_seed",
  "clientSeed": "client_seed_used",
  "nonce": 1,
  "game": "candle_flip",
  "betId": "BET_ID"
}

### Create Deposit Request (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/deposits
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "currency": "USDC",
  "amount": "100.00",
  "provider": "coinbase",
  "txRef": "tx_123456789"
}

### Process Deposit Webhook
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/deposits/provider/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "coinbase",
  "payload": {
    "txRef": "tx_123456789",
    "status": "confirmed",
    "amount": "100.00",
    "currency": "USDC"
  }
}

### Get User Deposits (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/deposits?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Create Withdrawal Request (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/withdrawals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "currency": "USDC",
  "amount": "50.00",
  "address": "0x1234567890123456789012345678901234567890"
}

### Get User Withdrawals (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/withdrawals?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Get Pending Withdrawals (admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/withdrawals/pending?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Get Daily Leaderboard
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/leaderboard/daily?limit=100

### Get User Leaderboard Position (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/leaderboard/position
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Get User Leaderboard History (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/leaderboard/history?days=30
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

